data.description: $5,000 SELLER PAID CLOSING COSTS FOR BUYER!!! About 10 Minutes to the Water in Swansboro and another 10 to the Beaches of Emerald Isle! Three Bedrooms and Two Full Baths with All Kitchen Appliances Convey with this Easy to Maintain Lawn Tucked Away from the Busy of the City on a Private Road! Home Received Architectural Shingles in 2020, New HVAC with Duct Work in 2020, New Commodes in 2020, New Water Heater in 2020, and All New Floors in 2020! With a Little Paint and some Love, this House Will Be Your Perfect Home!
